
ICloWidget : interface to all the widget
   void set_mode()  : change the widget mode ModeNormal|ModeSlime|ModeConnect)
   CloWidget::CloWidgetMode get_supported_mode() : return the list of all supported mode for a widget


CloWidget::Slider : a simple slider
CloWidget::Area : a container who re-arange his child
CloWidget::Knob : a knob
CloWidget::Text : a text zone
CloWidget::Button : a simple button
CloWidget::Pad : control x/y
CloWidget::Crossfader : a simple crossfader

